{"tid":1506887,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"戴耀廷：03年至今本港社運根源圍繞對雙普選訴求","createTime":"2019-08-26T02:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:00:28.000Z","uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a30175283febc83dc85cfe072a93f21c54ca3c8","tid":1506887,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476826-20190826.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476826-20190826.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxn88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=e741a416\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476826-20190826.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=26831be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476826-20190826.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n申請保釋等候上訴獲批的佔中發起人、港大法律系副教授戴耀廷說，香港情況較特別，涉及中國以至國際層面，所以很難從一般國際情況，推算香港今次抗爭的結果。不過，他認為近日警民衝突不斷提升，警察變成政府及示威者的磨心，政府高層需要解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n他出席一個電台的節目時說，市民對示威者使用暴力的接受程度愈來愈高，問題在於市民覺得政權缺乏正當性，若果政府解決不到這個問題，示威者的抗爭活動不會停止。<br />\n<br />\n他說不會焦聚於今次運動如何完結，認為整個反修例運動是香港民主運動的重要階段，由2003年的社運至今次運動的根源，都是圍繞香港人對雙普選的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1476826_1_20190826102455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1476826_1_20190826102455.jpg&h=636c5d59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48c44364d76c9cc4a74f68b62d3617849172ee58","tid":1506887,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］大家唔好再嘈啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464495</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}